1.title: About the course

episode of.title: Introducing our Enemy- the Dark Side (TV Series 2015– )

1.plot: In this course I will explain what the Dark Side or darkness really is. As a by product you will also understand what the Light really is. The hues white and black are widely used to depict opposites. Visually, white and black offer a high contrast. In Western culture, white and black traditionally symbolize the dichotomy of good and evil, metaphorically related to light and darkness.
